OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fnight will remain dry with clear
OL,8,Fperiods across the north and east.
OL,9,FBrisk winds along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FMainly dry and cloudy,
OL,12,Fchance of some occasional brightness.
OL,13,FPatchy rain likely to spread east
OL,14,Flater in the day. Mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FBright spells and a few showers on
OL,18,FThursday, but some dry spells of
OL,19,Fweather too. Chance of early rain on
OL,20,FFriday, otherwise mainly dry. Dry for
OL,21,Fmost Saturday.
